家。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nelly-responds-to-backlash-over-performing-at-donald-trump-liberty-ball-inauguration-3830420">Soulja Boy</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nelly-defends-playing-donald-trumps-inauguration-im-doing-this-because-its-an-honour-3830192">Nelly</a>都为自己在周末表演的选择进行了辩护，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">Snoop Dogg</a> 、 <a href="https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1126126582213579&amp;id=100044487427351">Village People</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billy-ray-cyrus-disastrous-performance-at-trump-inauguration-3830691">Billy Ray Cyrus</a>也因与庆祝活动的联系而成为话题。</p><p>就职典礼上另一位备受瞩目的人物是<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/elon-musk">埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-sparks-backlash-with-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3830625">他在人群面前做出了一个有争议的手势</a>，即他将手臂伸直向上，手掌朝下。许多人将这一手势比作纳粹敬礼，马斯克称其“令人厌倦”，是一种“肮脏的伎俩”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jewel-responds-to-backlash-after-playing-trump-inauguration-event-i-want-to-be-a-ray-of-light-in-this-world-3831957">朱厄尔在参加特朗普就职典礼后回应强烈反对：“我想成为这个世界上的一束光”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
